             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am an officer, I was sent for on the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178804020050"></xptr>prisoner's being stopped, and took him before a magistrate, and he was committed.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing of the matter.</p>
